---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Why Choose WEIGU | Heat Treatment Furnace Accessory Expert">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-4">Precision & Reliability</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 mb-8 leading-tight">Why Choose WEIGU?</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 mb-12">
        <p>At WEIGU, we don't just sell accessories; we provide the stability your heat treatment furnace needs to operate at peak efficiency. With over 20 years of expertise and a focus on zero-risk procurement, we have become the trusted partner for over 500 factories worldwide.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Exclusive Carburizing Solutions</h2>
          <p>We are a market leader in carburizing furnace parts, offering exclusive atmosphere control kits and methanol droppers that you won't find anywhere else.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">30% Better Value</h2>
          <p>Our ceramic fiber series and thermal insulation products are priced up to 30% lower than major competitors without compromising on quality.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="bg-gray-50 p-10 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-6">Our Core Advantages</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">✔</span> <strong>Zero-Risk Procurement:</strong> Standardized and verified components.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">✔</span> <strong>Global Logistics:</strong> Fast shipping via DHL/FedEx and optimized sea freight.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">✔</span> <strong>Technical Support:</strong> Expert guidance for atmosphere control and temperature measurement.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a href="/about-us/" class="text-orange-600 font-bold underline italic">Learn More About WEIGU →</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
